Competition in Focus is the monthly magazine on Current Affairs and General Knowledge and is useful for all those preparing for Civil Services, Bank Exams, NDA or any other competitive exam that has section on GK. The magazine captures current affairs through columns like News Reflections, Exam Shooters and Hot Spot. It also focuses on prominent and latest news of national and international interest in sections such as Inspot Light, World News, Info Crux and News Nector.
